<section class="about-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">{{ page.title | default: 'The PostureTru Story' }}</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      Why we created the posture corrector for remote workers.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Founder Story -->
<section class="section-padding">
  <div class="container about-section">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>It Started with Pain</h2>
      <p style="font-style: italic; color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: 20px;">Kartik Sachdeva, Founder</p>
      <p>PostureTru was born from personal pain, literally.</p>
      <p>Kartik spent years working from home, hunched over a laptop. By age 30, chronic back pain was affecting his work productivity, his sleep, and his overall health. He tried everything: expensive orthopedic harnesses, physical therapy, and frequent chiropractor visits.</p>
      <p>Nothing gave lasting relief.</p>
      <p>Then he realized something. The real problem was not strength or flexibility. It was awareness. He simply could not feel himself slouching until it had already happened. Once he started getting a gentle reminder the moment his posture slipped, paying attention became second nature, and his posture started to follow.</p>
      <p>Kartik thought: <em>"Why isn't there a simple, comfortable device that just tells you when you're slouching, nothing more, nothing less?"</em></p>
      <p>So Kartik built one and PostureTru was born.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-img-frame">
      <!-- SVG depicting founder spine alignment journey -->
      <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#F8FAF9" rx="12"/>
        <!-- Before silhouette (red/slouched) -->
        <g opacity="0.4">
          <path d="M120,80 Q105,150 70,220 L130,220 Q145,150 140,80 Z" fill="#E8D8CD"/>
          <circle cx="118" cy="80" r="18" fill="#E8D8CD"/>
          <path d="M120,130 Q80,170 100,210" fill="none" stroke="#C0392B" stroke-width="4"/>
          <text x="110" y="250" font-family="Outfit" font-size="14" fill="#C0392B" text-anchor="middle">Before</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Action Arrow -->
        <path d="M180,150 L220,150 M210,140 L220,150 L210,160" stroke="#1B4965" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>

        <!-- After silhouette (green/straight) -->
        <g>
          <path d="M280,80 Q280,150 280,220 L340,220 Q340,150 340,80 Z" fill="#E8D8CD"/>
          <circle cx="310" cy="80" r="18" fill="#E8D8CD"/>
          <path d="M310,120 L310,210" stroke="#5FB878" stroke-width="4"/>
          <!-- Active corrector indicator -->
          <rect x="295" y="135" width="30" height="40" fill="#1B4965" rx="3"/>
          <circle cx="310" cy="155" r="4" fill="#5FB878"/>
          <text x="310" y="250" font-family="Outfit" font-size="14" fill="#5FB878" text-anchor="middle">With PostureTru</text>
        </g>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission Statement -->
<section class="section-padding" style="background-color: var(--color-bg-light); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="container about-section">
    <div class="about-img-frame" style="background: var(--color-white);">
      <!-- SVG representing desk health -->
      <svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="#FFFFFF" rx="12"/>
        <rect x="80" y="200" width="240" height="15" fill="#2C3E50" rx="3"/>
        <rect x="190" y="215" width="20" height="50" fill="#7F8C8D"/>
        <rect x="150" y="265" width="100" height="8" fill="#7F8C8D" rx="4"/>
        <rect x="230" y="80" width="70" height="90" rx="6" fill="#F0F4F8" stroke="#E8ECEB" stroke-width="2"/>
        <line x1="245" y1="100" x2="285" y2="100" stroke="#1B4965" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <line x1="245" y1="120" x2="275" y2="120" stroke="#1B4965" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <line x1="245" y1="140" x2="280" y2="140" stroke="#1B4965" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <!-- Shield overlapping -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="150" r="35" fill="#5FB878"/>
        <path d="M190,148 L197,155 L212,142" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>Long hours at a desk make it easy to lose track of your posture without even noticing.</p>
      <p>Most posture solutions on the market are uncomfortable, overly restrictive, expensive, or simply do not lead to lasting change. PostureTru exists to change that.</p>
      <p>We believe every remote worker deserves:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>A comfortable solution that actually works under clothes</li>
        <li>Affordable, premium wellness technology</li>
        <li>Attentive support from a company that gets it</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 20px;">We are not a generic health conglomerate. We are remote workers who understand your pain, literally.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why Choose Us -->
<section class="section-padding" style="background-color: var(--color-bg);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Why Choose PostureTru</h2>
      <p>Our guiding values in wellness development.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <!-- Col 1 -->
      <div class="pillar-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Built for Remote Work</h3>
        <p>We work from home. We understand the specific setup hazards, the long sedentary stretches, and what it takes to remain healthy at a desk.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 2 -->
      <div class="pillar-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Premium Quality, Fair Price</h3>
        <p>We skip middleman markups. By selling directly, we use food grade silicone, imported ABS components, and a high precision gyroscope chip while keeping prices affordable.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Col 3 -->
      <div class="pillar-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Built Around Awareness</h3>
        <p>Every part of PostureTru is built around a simple idea. The gyroscope inside tracks your posture in real time and delivers a gentle reminder the moment you begin to slouch, so awareness becomes part of your day instead of something you have to think about.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

